msgid "Import Files"
msgstr "Uvezi datoteke"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../files.rst:40
msgid ""
"There are many different ways to import media files into an OpenShot "
"project. When a file is imported successfully, it will be automatically "
"selected and scrolled into view (in the **Project Files** panel). Also, if "
"the **Project Files** panel is not currently visible, OpenShot will "
"automatically display the panel."
msgstr ""
"Postoji mnogo različitih načina za uvoz medijskih datoteka u OpenShot "
"projekt. Kada je datoteka uspješno uvezena, automatski će biti odabrana i "
"prikazana u pogledu (u panelu **Datoteke projekta**). Također, ako panel "
"**Datoteke projekta** trenutno nije vidljiv, OpenShot će ga automatski "
"prikazati."

